manifest_analysis.title:
Clear text traffic is Enabled For App
[android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: The app intends to use cleartext network traffic, such as cleartext HTTP, FTP stacks, DownloadManager, and MediaPlayer. The default value for apps that target API level 27 or lower is "true". Apps that target API level 28 or higher default to "false". The key reason for avoiding cleartext traffic is the lack of confidentiality, authenticity, and protections against tampering; a network attacker can eavesdrop on transmitted data and also modify it without being detected.
manifest_analysis.name: Clear text traffic is Enabled For App [android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]

playstore_details.title: Zelcore - Multi Asset Crypto Wallet
playstore_details.description:
Zelcore - your browser to the blockchain. The single non-custodial platform for managing all your crypto world!

- More than 50 unique blockchains integrated
- More than 270 native assets integrated
- Tens of thousands of tokens natively available
- All top10 and majority of top100 assets
- Imports of tokens:
  -> Any Ethereum ERC20 Token
  -> Any Binance Smart Chain BEP20 Token
  -> Any Tron TRC10 Token
  -> Any Tron TRC20 Token
- Multiple wallet support
- Import your own wallet
- Quickswap exchanges: Changelly, Coinswitch, InstaSwap and Kyber
- Full API exchanges: Binance, Kraken, Bittrex, Stex, Gemini, KuCoin, Binance DEX
- No fees, free easy to use!
- Wallet Connect
- Buy crypto currencies without KYC with your credit card!
- Coin graphs and performance
- simple yet secure design and familiar design of username and password
- fully non-custodial, non-tracking!
- built in proxy servers
- Zel ID - your unique identity let's you log into additional services
- d2FA - your decentralised 2 factor authentication
- Available on all major desktop and mobile platforms
- Multi language platform
- 24/7 community support via Discord server
- Portfolio Tracker
- FluxNodes management
- FiroNodes management
- Message signing
- Biometrics login - fingerprint, face ID
- Easy sign login
- News aggregation
- Asset informations
- Contacts management
- Custom Backgrounds
- Custom Avatars
- Notifications
and many more!

Do you want to see your asset in zelcore? Missing some feature? Have a question? Simple. Contact us and we will do our best to add it!

Privacy Policy: https://zel.network/privacy/

Note: 
Some countries like Russia have restricted access to some international servers. Please use built in proxy server such as Singapore or Czech Republic.
